			<h1 class="page-title">Minor in Spanish for the Professions</h1>



<div id="textcontainer" class="page_content">

<div class="sidebar">
	<div id="sidebar-contact">








	</div>
</div>

<p>Students from other disciplines who want to pursue the Minor in Spanish for the Professions must complete a minimum of 15 semester hours as outlined below.</p>
